    "• Student made a noticeable deviation or error, and tutor bot pointed it out Regarding the nature of the conversations between the tutor bot and the students, most student responses did not contain factual errors that required correction.",
    "In such cases, where students generally provided accurate answers, it is understandable that the tutor bot's role in error correction would be limited.",
    "Given that the participants were graduate students, it is expected that their proficiency and accuracy in responses would be higher than those of novice learners.",
    "Consequently, the focus of the tutor bot's role may shift more towards providing additional insights, clarifications, or advanced explanations rather than correcting errors.",
    "Nonetheless, it remains important to offer meaningful feedback or guidance, even when errors are minimal."
